OL,3,GCentral, Tayside & Fife
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FAll parts will have a dry day.
OL,6,FCloud breaking this morning to leave
OL,7,Fsome sunshine for the rest of the day,
OL,8,Fbut may return to the Angus later this
OL,9,Fafternoon.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FThis evening will be dry with
OL,12,Fcloud spreading inland. Then the rest
OL,13,Fof the night will be dry and cloudy.
OL,14,FClearer across western Tayside until
OL,15,Flater.
OL,16,
OL,17,CWednesday:FA dry day. Overnight cloud
OL,18,Fwill gradually lift and break to allow
OL,19,Fsome sunny intervals by afternoon.
OL,20,FBest of the sunshine across western
OL,21,FTayside and Stirling.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
